<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8" standalone="yes"?><rss version="2.0" xmlns:atom="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom"><channel><title>Type-Narrowing on ErrorCode — Error Code Reference &amp; Solutions</title><link>https://errorcode.excellentwiki.com/tags/type-narrowing/</link><description>Recent content in Type-Narrowing on ErrorCode — Error Code Reference &amp; Solutions</description><generator>Hugo</generator><language>en</language><atom:link href="https://errorcode.excellentwiki.com/tags/type-narrowing/index.xml" rel="self" type="application/rss+xml"/><item><title>[Solution] TypeScript TS18046 — 'X' Is of Type 'unknown'</title><link>https://errorcode.excellentwiki.com/languages/typescript/ts18046/</link><pubDate>Mon, 01 Jan 0001 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://errorcode.excellentwiki.com/languages/typescript/ts18046/</guid><description>&lt;h1 id="ts18046--x-is-of-type-unknown"&gt;TS18046 — &amp;lsquo;X&amp;rsquo; is of type &amp;lsquo;unknown&amp;rsquo;&lt;/h1&gt;
&lt;p&gt;TS18046 occurs when you try to use a value typed as &lt;code&gt;unknown&lt;/code&gt; without first narrowing its type. The &lt;code&gt;unknown&lt;/code&gt; type is TypeScript&amp;rsquo;s type-safe alternative to &lt;code&gt;any&lt;/code&gt; — you must verify the type before accessing properties or methods.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2 id="common-causes"&gt;Common Causes&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;div class="highlight"&gt;&lt;pre tabindex="0" style="color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;-webkit-text-size-adjust:none;"&gt;&lt;code class="language-typescript" data-lang="typescript"&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;// Cause 1: Catch clause variable is unknown by default
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;try&lt;/span&gt; {
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;throw&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;new&lt;/span&gt; Error(&lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;&amp;#34;fail&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt;);
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;} &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;catch&lt;/span&gt; (&lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;e&lt;/span&gt;) {
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;console&lt;/span&gt;.&lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;log&lt;/span&gt;(&lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;e&lt;/span&gt;.&lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;message&lt;/span&gt;); &lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;// TS18046: &amp;#39;e&amp;#39; is of type &amp;#39;unknown&amp;#39;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;}
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;// Cause 2: Using unknown from a generic
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;function&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;parse&lt;/span&gt;&amp;lt;&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;T&lt;/span&gt;&amp;gt;(&lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;input&lt;/span&gt;: &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;unknown&lt;/span&gt;)&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;:&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;T&lt;/span&gt; {
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;return&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;input&lt;/span&gt;; &lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;// TS18046 if you try to access input properties
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;}
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;// Cause 3: Fetching untyped data
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;const&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;response&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;=&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;await&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;fetch&lt;/span&gt;(&lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;&amp;#34;/api&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt;);
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;const&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;data&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;=&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;await&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;response&lt;/span&gt;.&lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;json&lt;/span&gt;(); &lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;// data is &amp;#39;any&amp;#39;, but if typed as &amp;#39;unknown&amp;#39;...
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;console&lt;/span&gt;.&lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;log&lt;/span&gt;(&lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;data&lt;/span&gt;.&lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;name&lt;/span&gt;); &lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;// TS18046
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;// Cause 4: Value from a Map with unknown value type
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;const&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;map&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;=&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;new&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;Map&lt;/span&gt;&amp;lt;&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;string&lt;/span&gt;, &lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;unknown&lt;/span&gt;&amp;gt;();
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;const&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;val&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;=&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;map&lt;/span&gt;.&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;get&lt;/span&gt;(&lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;&amp;#34;key&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt;);
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;console&lt;/span&gt;.&lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;log&lt;/span&gt;(&lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;val&lt;/span&gt;.&lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;toString&lt;/span&gt;()); &lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;// TS18046
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;h2 id="solutions"&gt;Solutions&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;h3 id="fix-1-use-a-type-guard-to-narrow-the-type"&gt;Fix 1: Use a type guard to narrow the type&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;div class="highlight"&gt;&lt;pre tabindex="0" style="color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;-webkit-text-size-adjust:none;"&gt;&lt;code class="language-typescript" data-lang="typescript"&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;// Wrong
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;try&lt;/span&gt; {
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;throw&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;new&lt;/span&gt; Error(&lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;&amp;#34;fail&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt;);
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;} &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;catch&lt;/span&gt; (&lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;e&lt;/span&gt;) {
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;console&lt;/span&gt;.&lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;log&lt;/span&gt;(&lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;e&lt;/span&gt;.&lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;message&lt;/span&gt;); &lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;// TS18046
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;}
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;// Correct
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;try&lt;/span&gt; {
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;throw&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;new&lt;/span&gt; Error(&lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;&amp;#34;fail&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt;);
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;} &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;catch&lt;/span&gt; (&lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;e&lt;/span&gt;) {
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;if&lt;/span&gt; (&lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;e&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;instanceof&lt;/span&gt; Error) {
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;console&lt;/span&gt;.&lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;log&lt;/span&gt;(&lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;e&lt;/span&gt;.&lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;message&lt;/span&gt;); &lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;// OK — e is Error
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; }
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;}
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;h3 id="fix-2-use-typeof-checks-for-primitives"&gt;Fix 2: Use typeof checks for primitives&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;div class="highlight"&gt;&lt;pre tabindex="0" style="color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;-webkit-text-size-adjust:none;"&gt;&lt;code class="language-typescript" data-lang="typescript"&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;function&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;process&lt;/span&gt;(&lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;value&lt;/span&gt;: &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;unknown&lt;/span&gt;) {
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;if&lt;/span&gt; (&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;typeof&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;value&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;===&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;&amp;#34;string&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt;) {
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;console&lt;/span&gt;.&lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;log&lt;/span&gt;(&lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;value&lt;/span&gt;.&lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;toUpperCase&lt;/span&gt;()); &lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;// OK — value is string
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; }
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;}
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;h3 id="fix-3-use-type-assertions-when-you-know-the-type"&gt;Fix 3: Use type assertions when you know the type&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;div class="highlight"&gt;&lt;pre tabindex="0" style="color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;-webkit-text-size-adjust:none;"&gt;&lt;code class="language-typescript" data-lang="typescript"&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;const&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;data&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;=&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;await&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;response&lt;/span&gt;.&lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;json&lt;/span&gt;() &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;as&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;User&lt;/span&gt;;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;console&lt;/span&gt;.&lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;log&lt;/span&gt;(&lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;data&lt;/span&gt;.&lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;name&lt;/span&gt;); &lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;// OK
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;h3 id="fix-4-use-a-validated-parsing-library"&gt;Fix 4: Use a validated parsing library&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;div class="highlight"&gt;&lt;pre tabindex="0" style="color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;-webkit-text-size-adjust:none;"&gt;&lt;code class="language-typescript" data-lang="typescript"&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;import&lt;/span&gt; { &lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;z&lt;/span&gt; } &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;from&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;&amp;#34;zod&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt;;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;const&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;UserSchema&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;=&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;z&lt;/span&gt;.&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;object&lt;/span&gt;({
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;name&lt;/span&gt;: &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;z.string&lt;/span&gt;(),
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;age&lt;/span&gt;: &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;z.number&lt;/span&gt;(),
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;});
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;const&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;data&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;=&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;UserSchema&lt;/span&gt;.&lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;parse&lt;/span&gt;(&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;await&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;response&lt;/span&gt;.&lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;json&lt;/span&gt;());
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;console&lt;/span&gt;.&lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;log&lt;/span&gt;(&lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;data&lt;/span&gt;.&lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;name&lt;/span&gt;); &lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;// OK — typed as { name: string; age: number }
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;h2 id="examples"&gt;Examples&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;div class="highlight"&gt;&lt;pre tabindex="0" style="color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;-webkit-text-size-adjust:none;"&gt;&lt;code class="language-typescript" data-lang="typescript"&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;// Example 1: forEach with unknown
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;const&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;items&lt;/span&gt;: &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;unknown&lt;/span&gt;[] &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;=&lt;/span&gt; [&lt;span style="color:#ae81ff"&gt;1&lt;/span&gt;, &lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;&amp;#34;hello&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt;, &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;true&lt;/span&gt;];
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;items&lt;/span&gt;.&lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;forEach&lt;/span&gt;(&lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;item&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;=&amp;gt;&lt;/span&gt; {
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;console&lt;/span&gt;.&lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;log&lt;/span&gt;(&lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;item&lt;/span&gt;.&lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;toFixed&lt;/span&gt;()); &lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;// TS18046
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;});
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;// Fix:
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;items&lt;/span&gt;.&lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;forEach&lt;/span&gt;(&lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;item&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;=&amp;gt;&lt;/span&gt; {
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;if&lt;/span&gt; (&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;typeof&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;item&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;===&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;&amp;#34;number&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt;) {
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;console&lt;/span&gt;.&lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;log&lt;/span&gt;(&lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;item&lt;/span&gt;.&lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;toFixed&lt;/span&gt;()); &lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;// OK
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; }
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;});
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;// Example 2: JSON.parse returns any, but explicit unknown needs narrowing
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;const&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;parsed&lt;/span&gt;: &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;unknown&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;=&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;JSON&lt;/span&gt;.&lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;parse&lt;/span&gt;(&lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;&amp;#39;{&amp;#34;x&amp;#34;: 10}&amp;#39;&lt;/span&gt;);
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;console&lt;/span&gt;.&lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;log&lt;/span&gt;(&lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;parsed&lt;/span&gt;.&lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;x&lt;/span&gt;); &lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;// TS18046
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;h2 id="related-errors"&gt;Related Errors&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="https://errorcode.excellentwiki.com/languages/typescript/ts7006/"&gt;TS7006: Parameter implicitly has &amp;lsquo;any&amp;rsquo; type&lt;/a&gt; — the opposite: no type at all vs strict unknown.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="https://errorcode.excellentwiki.com/languages/typescript/ts2322/"&gt;TS2322: Type is not assignable&lt;/a&gt; — broader assignability issues.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="https://errorcode.excellentwiki.com/languages/typescript/ts2531/"&gt;TS2531: Object is possibly &amp;rsquo;null&amp;rsquo;&lt;/a&gt; — similar narrowing needed for null.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;</description></item><item><title>[Solution] TypeScript TS2339 v2 — Property Does Not Exist on Type Fix</title><link>https://errorcode.excellentwiki.com/languages/typescript/ts2339-error-v2/</link><pubDate>Mon, 01 Jan 0001 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://errorcode.excellentwiki.com/languages/typescript/ts2339-error-v2/</guid><description>&lt;h1 id="ts2339--property-does-not-exist-on-type-v2"&gt;TS2339 — Property Does Not Exist on Type (v2)&lt;/h1&gt;
&lt;p&gt;This variant of TS2339 covers situations where property access fails on union types, generic constraints, or when working with third-party library types that lack proper typings.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2 id="what-this-error-means"&gt;What This Error Means&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Common error messages:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;code&gt;TS2339: Property 'name' does not exist on type 'User | null'&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;code&gt;TS2339: Property 'data' does not exist on type 'unknown'&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;code&gt;TS2339: Property 'map' does not exist on type 'T'&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;code&gt;TS2339: Property 'toISOString' does not exist on type 'string | Date'&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;TypeScript prevents accessing properties that the current type annotation doesn&amp;rsquo;t include. This often happens after narrowing, with union types, or when the type is inferred as &lt;code&gt;unknown&lt;/code&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;</description></item><item><title>[Solution] TypeScript TS2367 v2 — Comparison Appears Unintentional Fix</title><link>https://errorcode.excellentwiki.com/languages/typescript/ts2367-error-v2/</link><pubDate>Mon, 01 Jan 0001 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://errorcode.excellentwiki.com/languages/typescript/ts2367-error-v2/</guid><description>&lt;h1 id="ts2367--comparison-appears-unintentional-v2"&gt;TS2367 — Comparison Appears Unintentional (v2)&lt;/h1&gt;
&lt;p&gt;This variant of TS2367 covers comparisons between types that are provably unequal, including literal type comparisons, boolean checks against non-boolean values, and exhaustive switch statements.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2 id="what-this-error-means"&gt;What This Error Means&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Common error messages:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;code&gt;TS2367: This comparison appears to be unintentional because the types '&amp;quot;admin&amp;quot;' and '&amp;quot;user&amp;quot;' have no overlap.&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;code&gt;TS2367: This comparison appears to be unintentional because the types 'boolean' and 'number' have no overlap.&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;code&gt;TS2367: This comparison appears to be unintentional because the types 'string' and 'number' have no overlap.&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;TypeScript detects when a comparison can never be true based on the types of the operands. This often means the comparison is redundant or there&amp;rsquo;s a bug in the logic.&lt;/p&gt;</description></item><item><title>[Solution] TypeScript Type 'never' Has No Properties — Exhaustive Check Fix</title><link>https://errorcode.excellentwiki.com/languages/typescript/never-type/</link><pubDate>Mon, 01 Jan 0001 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://errorcode.excellentwiki.com/languages/typescript/never-type/</guid><description>&lt;h1 id="typescript-type-never-has-no-properties"&gt;TypeScript: Type &amp;rsquo;never&amp;rsquo; has no properties&lt;/h1&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The &lt;code&gt;never&lt;/code&gt; type represents values that never occur — a function that always throws, or a variable that can never be assigned a value. When you see &amp;ldquo;Type &amp;rsquo;never&amp;rsquo; has no properties&amp;rdquo;, you are trying to access properties or call methods on a value that TypeScript has determined is unreachable. This is actually a powerful feature for exhaustive type checking.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2 id="common-causes"&gt;Common Causes&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Switch statement missing a case&lt;/strong&gt; — TypeScript narrows to &lt;code&gt;never&lt;/code&gt; when all cases are covered, but if you add a new case, the &lt;code&gt;never&lt;/code&gt; check catches it&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Dead code after return/throw&lt;/strong&gt; — code that TypeScript knows cannot execute&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Incorrect type narrowing&lt;/strong&gt; — a condition that TypeScript determines is impossible&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Generic default resolving to never&lt;/strong&gt; — a type parameter that defaults to &lt;code&gt;never&lt;/code&gt; is used directly&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;h2 id="how-to-fix"&gt;How to Fix&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;div class="highlight"&gt;&lt;pre tabindex="0" style="color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;-webkit-text-size-adjust:none;"&gt;&lt;code class="language-typescript" data-lang="typescript"&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;// Cause 1: Switch statement not exhaustive
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;type&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;Shape&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;=&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;&amp;#34;circle&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;|&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;&amp;#34;square&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;|&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;&amp;#34;triangle&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt;;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;function&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;area&lt;/span&gt;(&lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;shape&lt;/span&gt;: &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;Shape&lt;/span&gt;)&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;:&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;number&lt;/span&gt; {
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;switch&lt;/span&gt; (&lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;shape&lt;/span&gt;) {
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;case&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;&amp;#34;circle&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;:&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;return&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#ae81ff"&gt;3.14&lt;/span&gt;;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;case&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;&amp;#34;square&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;:&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;return&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#ae81ff"&gt;1&lt;/span&gt;;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;// Missing &amp;#34;triangle&amp;#34; case — no error here but adding it later causes issues
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; }
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;}
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;// Fix: use exhaustive check
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;function&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;area&lt;/span&gt;(&lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;shape&lt;/span&gt;: &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;Shape&lt;/span&gt;)&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;:&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;number&lt;/span&gt; {
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;switch&lt;/span&gt; (&lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;shape&lt;/span&gt;) {
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;case&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;&amp;#34;circle&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;:&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;return&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#ae81ff"&gt;3.14&lt;/span&gt;;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;case&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;&amp;#34;square&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;:&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;return&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#ae81ff"&gt;1&lt;/span&gt;;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;case&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;&amp;#34;triangle&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;:&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;return&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#ae81ff"&gt;0.5&lt;/span&gt;;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;default&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;:&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;const&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;_exhaustive&lt;/span&gt;: &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;never&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;=&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;shape&lt;/span&gt;; &lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;// compile error if case is missing
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;return&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;_exhaustive&lt;/span&gt;;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; }
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;}
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;// Cause 2: Accessing property on narrowed never
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;function&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;process&lt;/span&gt;(&lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;value&lt;/span&gt;: &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;string&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;|&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;number&lt;/span&gt;) {
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;if&lt;/span&gt; (&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;typeof&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;value&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;===&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;&amp;#34;string&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;&amp;amp;&amp;amp;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;typeof&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;value&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;===&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;&amp;#34;number&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt;) {
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;// This condition is impossible — value is &amp;#39;never&amp;#39; here
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;console&lt;/span&gt;.&lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;log&lt;/span&gt;(&lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;value&lt;/span&gt;.&lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;toUpperCase&lt;/span&gt;()); &lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;// TS2339: &amp;#39;never&amp;#39; has no property &amp;#39;toUpperCase&amp;#39;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; }
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;}
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;// Cause 3: Return type is never
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;function&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;throwError&lt;/span&gt;(&lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;msg&lt;/span&gt;: &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;string&lt;/span&gt;)&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;:&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;never&lt;/span&gt; {
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;throw&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;new&lt;/span&gt; Error(&lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;msg&lt;/span&gt;);
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;}
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;const&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;result&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;=&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;throwError&lt;/span&gt;(&lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;&amp;#34;oops&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt;);
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;result&lt;/span&gt;.&lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;foo&lt;/span&gt;; &lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;// TS2339: &amp;#39;never&amp;#39; has no property &amp;#39;foo&amp;#39;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;h2 id="examples"&gt;Examples&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;div class="highlight"&gt;&lt;pre tabindex="0" style="color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;-webkit-text-size-adjust:none;"&gt;&lt;code class="language-typescript" data-lang="typescript"&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;// Example 1: Exhaustive discriminated union check
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;interface&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;Circle&lt;/span&gt; { &lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;kind&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;:&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;&amp;#34;circle&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt;; &lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;radius&lt;/span&gt;: &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;number&lt;/span&gt;; }
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;interface&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;Square&lt;/span&gt; { &lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;kind&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;:&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;&amp;#34;square&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt;; &lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;side&lt;/span&gt;: &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;number&lt;/span&gt;; }
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;type&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;Shape&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;=&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;Circle&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;|&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;Square&lt;/span&gt;;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;function&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;describe&lt;/span&gt;(&lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;shape&lt;/span&gt;: &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;Shape&lt;/span&gt;)&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;:&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;string&lt;/span&gt; {
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;switch&lt;/span&gt; (&lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;shape&lt;/span&gt;.&lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;kind&lt;/span&gt;) {
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;case&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;&amp;#34;circle&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;:&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;return&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;`Circle with radius &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;${&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;shape&lt;/span&gt;.&lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;radius&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;}&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;`&lt;/span&gt;;
